items.value: A classic sweet treat! Gives a LOT of stamina, but slows you down!
The proudest student in Here School! He always tries to force his beliefs on others. Make sure to be respectful, or else...
In a world that often seeks to categorize and label,
the journey of discovering and embracing one's true self is nothing short of a remarkable act of courage.
For many transgender individuals, this journey is a path toward authenticity, self-love, and empowerment.
It is a story that deserves to be celebrated, highlighting the strength,
resilience, and beauty found within the trans community.
Did you just walk away like a transphobe?
